oton energies and higher fluences, reaching peak observed values of 15 % in\nTiN and 50 % in ZrN in the epsilon-near-zero window.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Apr 2020 19:40:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 May 2020 17:02:06 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 10 Jul 2020 22:04:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-29"}
