at flux and 10-times\nlower diffusion in ion heated case than predicted by the modeling. However, the\nCGYRO model correctly predicts that the Al diffusion dramatically increases\nbelow the linear threshold for the transition from the ion temperature gradient\n(ITG) to trapped electron mode (TEM).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Apr 2020 00:13:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-26"}
