oirs is not well-constrained and may contain a larger\nproportion of ferropericlase than what is allowed by our results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Apr 2020 02:06:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 23 Nov 2020 01:06:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-16"}
