nd three-body effective interactions to describe nuclear systems up\nto densities several times higher than the central density of atomic nuclei.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Apr 2020 15:15:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 27 Oct 2020 15:55:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-28"}
